    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>New President Named at Bozell</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Stuart Elliott</byline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Joan H. Walker has been named president at Bozell Public Relations in New York, effective immediately, succeeding Fred Thompson, 46, who left to pursue other interests, the agency said.</p>
        <p>Ms. Walker, 45, was previously managing director of marketing communications at the Nynex Corporation in New York. Before that, she was an executive vice president at Saatchi &amp; Saatchi in New York.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Joan H. Walker has been named president at Bozell Public Relations in New York, effective immediately, succeeding Fred Thompson, 46, who left to pursue other interests, the agency said.</p>
        <p>Ms. Walker, 45, was previously managing director of marketing communications at the Nynex Corporation in New York. Before that, she was an executive vice president at Saatchi &amp; Saatchi in New York.</p>
        <p>Also, Andrew Polansky, 31, an executive vice president at Bozell, has been named to the additional new position of general manager at the New York office.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
